Code.NativeIaC:
```bicep
resource vnet 'Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks@2023-09-01' = {
  name: '<example_resource_name>'
  location: '<example_location>'
  properties: {
    addressSpace: { addressPrefixes: ['10.0.0.0/16'] }
    enableDdosProtection: true // Critical: enables DDoS Protection
    ddosProtectionPlan: { id: '<example_resource_id>' }
  }
}
```

Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "azurerm_virtual_network" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name                = "<example_resource_name>"
  location            = "<example_resource_id>"
  resource_group_name = "<example_resource_id>"
  address_space       = ["10.0.0.0/16"]

  ddos_protection_plan {
    id     = "<example_resource_id>"  # Critical: associates DDoS Protection Plan
    enable = true
  }
}
```
